Detailed Description

template<typename InternalCharType__, typename SizeType__>
class fsdict::TransTable< TT_PERFHASH, InternalCharType__, SizeType__ >::State

This class provides a much easier interface to the dic if the guts of the automaton have to be explored state- and transition-wise.
